OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FBy Jack Abbey, ITV News Political
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FNew emergency measures to relieve
OL,10,Fovercrowding in English and Welsh
OL,11,Fprisons will come into effect from
OL,12,FTuesday, September 10, seeing
OL,13,Fthousands of prisoners released
OL,14,Fearlier than expected.
OL,16,FIn recent months the prison population
OL,17,Fhas repeatedly reached record highs,
OL,18,Fwith the most recent figures showing
OL,19,Fthe number of those in UK prisons had
OL,20,Fhit 88,521 people on Friday.
