OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FThat came only days after ITV News
OL,7,Freported that only 100 spaces were
OL,8,Fleft in male prisons in the UK,
OL,9,Ffollowing the August bank holiday
OL,10,Fweekend.
OL,12,FThe government are deeply concerned by
OL,13,Fwhat could happen if prison spaces run
OL,14,Fout.
OL,16,FLord Chancellor Shabana Mahmood, when
OL,17,Fshe announced the measures, warned
OL,18,Fthat police could even have to stop
OL,19,Fcarrying out arrests in a worst case
OL,20,Fscenario, possibly leading to looting
OL,21,Fand the collapse of law and order.
