OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FBut how will the measures work, and
OL,7,Fhow much risk do they pose?
OL,9,FIf you're impacted by these new plans
OL,10,Fplease get in touch with ITV News by
OL,11,Fsending an email to yourstory@itv.com.
OL,13,FWhat is the plan?
OL,15,FTo free up space in prisons, the
OL,16,Fgovernment announced in July that some
OL,17,Fprisoners would be released after
OL,18,Fserving only 40% of their sentence
OL,19,Frather than 50% - as required under
OL,20,Fprevious guidelines.
