OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FThe first set of prisoners to be
OL,7,Freleased from the September 10 are
OL,8,Fthose who were given sentences of five
OL,9,Fyears or less.
OL,11,FThere are exceptions, however. Those
OL,12,Fserving sentences for sex and violent
OL,13,Foffences are excluded, as are some
OL,14,Foffences related to domestic violence.
OL,16,FA total of 5,500 prisoners are
OL,17,Fexpected to be let out, along with a
OL,18,Fsecond release from October of those
OL,19,Fserving five years or more.
OL,21,FAre there risks?
