OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FYes. The justice secretary admitted as
OL,7,Fmuch when announcing the measures, and
OL,8,Fsince then, experts including the
OL,9,Fchief inspector of probation have
OL,10,Fwarned that the plans amount to
OL,11,F"rolling the dice".
OL,13,FConcerns centre around whether those
OL,14,Freleased will go onto reoffend, but
OL,15,Falso the strain releasing thousands of
OL,16,Fpeople early could put on services,
OL,17,Fincluding those for the homeless.
OL,19,FThe government insists that they have
OL,20,Fno other option and "do not take this
OL,21,Fdecision lightly".
