OL,3,CWhy are thousands of prisoners to be
OL,4,Creleased early from UK jails?
OL,6,FEven with new prisons being built,
OL,7,Fprojections show that prison
OL,8,Fpopulations will grow faster.
OL,10,FThis new scheme replaces a previous
OL,11,Fplan implemented by the last
OL,12,FConservative government in 2023 to
OL,13,Frelease some prisoners ten weeks early.
OL,15,FBut with warnings of prisons becoming
OL,16,Ffull within days, the new
OL,17,Fadministration felt they had to take
OL,18,Ffurther action.
